  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 325f (165c).",
    "in a small bowl, combine the yeast, salt, and 1 tablespoon of the olive oil to make the yeast paste.",
    "massage the lamb shoulder to loosen the fibers, then prick the surface with a fork to create holes for the marinade.",
    "rub the lamb all over with the yeast paste, then place it in a large bowl or zip-top plastic bag large enough to hold the lamb and the marinade."
  ],
